    <h4 class="h3">I will choose a no calorie beverage option, such as diet soda or tea</h4>

    <p>Sugared beverages can add unwanted calories to your daily diet — and those calories don’t contain any essential nutrients!  Some calories in drinks are also “hidden”, such as coffee drinks and juices.  Following is an example of how to save calories (in this case 650 calories!) just by replacing caloric beverages with non-caloric ones:</p>

